infra.display: ZYNQ-7S TE0726-*-07S-1C (512MB DDR). *SPRT PCB: REV03, REV02.
infra.description: ZYNQ-7S TE0726-*-07S-1C ZynqBerry Board (form factor like RPI2) with single ARM Cortex-A9, 512MB Memory, 100MBit Ethernet, speed grade -1 and commercial temperature range. *Supported PCB Revisions: REV03 and REV02. Note: primary boot device is QSPI, SD can be used as secondary boot device only.
